---
title: Beef Koftas & Tabbouleh Couscous with Hummus & Flaked Almonds
description: These koftas are handy parcels of flavour, with tender mince, mild spices and a smattering of almonds to add extra texture. Paired with a veggie-packed couscous tabbouleh and hummus, this is a Middle Eastern feast to remember.
